some exotic locales.

30:04.936 --> 30:07.839 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Economics correspondent Paul
Solman suffered through this
tough assignment, part of his

30:07.839 --> 30:09.741 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
weekly series, "Making Sense",
which airs Thursdays.

30:09.741 --> 30:12.077 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
