JEFFREY BROWN, PBS NEWSHOUR
CORRESPONDENT: Take another
look: that's the invitation from

42:28.613 --> 42:32.183 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
two Los Angeles museums,
together presenting a major
retrospective of the work of
Robert

42:32.183 --> 42:35.153 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Mapplethorpe.

42:35.153 --> 42:40.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
